The following is the structure of the folders

pwd/assets {
    Contains Image and Audio Assets(when i get some)
    they may be sorted into further subdirs
}

pwd/src {
    Contains all code necessary to compile
    again may be sorted into further subdirs
    src/gfx {
        All Graphics related source files
    }
    src/audio {
        All Audio related source files
    }
    src/input {
        All input related source files
    }
    src/gameplay {
        All gameplay related source files
    }
    src/physics {
        All physics related source files
    }
}

pwd/Makefile {
    Compiles the Program
}

pwd/_Structure_ {
    Contains Information about folder structures(ie this document)
}
